              <span id="reviewTextContainer714850740" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3188176802907167722">I always love stories of Merlin and Arthur and this series has been good so far, however it is disturbing to me that Merlin is Christian in these books. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

